Package org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak.Util

package org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak.Util
Group of Classes with general use in the program. Such as Fields, Responses, Tuples, Placements and Field probability. It's needed in all others packages as it defines the schema for communication. AIResponse is a Class that wraps the desired attack by AI. It can also be used to wrap the human input. Tuple is a simple tuple with 1 generic type. AprioriProb gives a number resembling probability to a Tuple with position. Field represent place on the board. Such if there is a ship, what type of ship, if it was hit and if the whole ship sunk. ShipPlacement is a class that wraps all information about where specific ship is to be placed on the board.
